libesmtp: libesmtp (Mail Transport Agent Library)
libesmtp:
libesmtp: libESMTP is an SMTP client which manages posting (or submission of) 
libesmtp: electronic mail via a preconfigured Mail Transport Agent (MTA). 
libesmtp: libESMTP supports many SMTP extensions, notably PIPELINING (RFC 2920), 
libesmtp: DSN (RFC 1891) and SASL authentication (RFC 2554). SMTP AUTH is 
libesmtp: implemented using a SASL client library integrated into libESMTP. 
libesmtp:
